            "text": "4662 - وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "سَأَلَ سَعْدُ بْنُ سَعْدٍ اَلرِّضَا عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ :"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " عَنِ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "اَلصَّبِيِّ هَلْ يُرْضَعُ أَكْثَرَ مِنْ سَنَتَيْنِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:47:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/47/2",
      "text": [
        " \"عَامَيْنِ\" قُلْتُ فَإِنْ زَادَ عَلَى سَنَتَيْنِ هَلْ عَلَى أَبَوَيْهِ مِنْ ذَلِكَ شَيْءٌ قَالَ \"لاَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4662 - Sa'd ibn Sa'd asked Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) about whether a child can be breastfed for more than two years.\nImam (as) replied: \"Two years.\"\nI asked: \"If it exceeds two years, is there any obligation upon the parents because of that?\"\nImam (as) said: \"No.\""
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
